trans-unit.source: Specifies the state of an axis.
The AxisEnabled enumeration is used with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A> property to enable or disable an axis.
trans-unit.target: AxisEnabled 열거형 사용한는 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>축을 사용 하지 않도록 설정 하거나 사용 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A> property is set to Auto, an axis may or may not be displayed, depending on whether it is being used to plot a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>.
trans-unit.target: 경우에 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>자동으로 속성을 설정 하면 축이 표시 되거나 표시 되지 않을를 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> 를 그리는 데 사용 되 고 있는지 여부에 따라</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Enabled%2A>

trans-unit.source: The axes that are used to plot data for a series are determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A> property settings.
trans-unit.target: 계열 데이터를 그리는 데 사용 되는 축에 의해 결정 됩니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A>속성 설정을.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YAxisType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XAxisType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The axis is only enabled if it used to plot a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 축이를 그리는 데 사용 하는 경우에 사용는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series"> </xref>합니다.
